article_id:1082,category_name:Maintenance,title_name:Maintenance Notice for 2/25 (PT) [Update],image_path:,message:<div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582696800"></span>]</strong></span><br>The maintenance is now complete.<br><br>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send the following items to all players who started playing before <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582691340"></span>.<br><br>・Exquisite Honey x2<br>・Blessed Ethon Ashes x2<br><br>These items can be claimed from your goodie box for up to 7 days after reception.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><hr><div>We will be performing maintenance during the following period in order to prepare for the next update.</div><div>You will not be able to obtain rewards if you complete a quest during the maintenance period. Please also claim any 30-Day Pack (Recovery) rewards before maintenance begins.</div><div><br></div><div>■Maintenance Period</div><div>Around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582691400"></span> to around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1582696800"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The game will be inaccessible during maintenance.</div><div>2. Maintenance may start and/or end before or after the scheduled times.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1582092000,update_time1582696836